:<font size="15">דּגל</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
דּגל / dâgal / daw-gal'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''דּגל'''

# To flaunt, that is, raise a flag; figuratively to be conspicuous: - (set up, with) banners, chiefest.

